code: @Parameterized.Parameters public static Collection<Object[]> data() {     return Arrays.asList(new Object[][] { { new SavepointInfo("/tmp", null) }, { new SavepointInfo(null, new SerializedThrowable(new RuntimeException("expected"))) } }). }
@Override protected SavepointInfo getTestResponseInstance() throws Exception {     return savepointInfo. }
